      "id": "1000229",
      "title": "",
      "description": "\u2022 Local and express shuttle buses will be available.\r\n\r\n\u2022 This is to accommodate signal improvement work.\r\n\r\n\u2022 A diversion schedule will be in effect.\r\n\r\n\u2022 An express shuttle will operate nonstop between North Station and Swampscott.\r\n\r\n\u2022 A local shuttle will operate between North Station and Swampscott, making all local stops.\r\n\r\n\u2022 Riders using the shuttle buses should budget extra travel time. For example, a rider traveling to North Station from Swampscott should budget up to 40 minutes additional travel on the express shuttle and up to 70 minutes additional travel on the local shuttle.\r\n\r\nShuttle bus pick-up/drop-off locations:\r\n\r\nNorth Station:\r\nNashua St @ Red Auerbach Way\r\n\r\nChelsea:\r\nInbound, Everett Ave @ Vale St (MBTA Route 112 bus stop). Outbound, Everett Ave @ Maple St (MBTA Route 112 bus stop).\r\n\r\nWonderland:\r\nWonderland Blue Line Station Busway (behind Berth E)\r\n\r\nLynn:\r\nLynn Station Busway Berth #1 (MBTA Routes 441 & 442 bus stop)\r\n\r\nSwampscott:\r\nRailroad Ave @ Swampscott Station",
